content:
To get the latest metrics about your contact center, open Amazon Connectâ€™s Real-Time Metrics dashboard directly from Omni Supervisor. The dashboard shows key metrics such as the agents online, handled and abandoned calls, and more.

Required user permissions:
Contact Center Admin to set up 
Assign User's Profile to Supervisor Configuration Settings to view 

Available with Service Cloud Voice using Amazon Connect, Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect, or Partner Telephony.

Add AWS Dashboard action to Omni Supervisor tabs.
Click View Amazon Real-Time Metrics on any tab in Omni Supervisor.
The default actions also show on Omni Supervisor tabs.
title: Viewing Real-Time Metrics in Service Cloud Voice
